 the frames a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"patch covered live). The measured FRR is always scored against the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"original gallery — patches never inflate it. Cancel discards the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"patches."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Hosts should run this between gallery completion and persisting","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the tracker, surface the rate to the user, and persist regardless","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the result (recommend a re-enrol on a low unpatched rate rather","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"than failing the save — reject loops strand users).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Returns ","type":"text"},{"code":".trackerIsNull","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when the identity isn’t enrolled or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"another session owns the embedding feed (also the constant return","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for engines without the verification walk, e.g. Luxand).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk\/beginenrollmentverification(identity:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/YEOFRSDK/beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)":{"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk\/beginenrollmentverification(identity:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"beginEnrollmentVerification"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"identity"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"FRSDKReturnCode","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.y